***If you get following error : ***



***First check the Ubuntu version :***
lsb_release -a

I had received error as Ubuntu 20.04.6 had some library compatibility issues .

So I have used rstudio-2024.12.1-563-amd64.deb for Rstudio installation .

which rstudio

sudo apt autoremove

sudo apt purge rstudio

sudo dpkg -i rstudio-2024.12.1-563-amd64.deb

sudo apt -f install

ldd --version

ls /usr/bin/rstudio

rstudio

This should resolve issues . 
